{"tid":346612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街，地鐵又壞車","createTime":"2017-08-04T05:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T04:28:29.000Z","uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8423c9f7f862f45c118e7f1aea1008f1fe5837fc","tid":346612,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"坐坐下無啦啦有廣播話搶修"},{"pid":"590552b273b152560f41a6972a458c057ce95250","tid":346612,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價又識得加"},{"pid":"450d3f26c783cd90baba4d303b319d0215ad96d6","tid":346612,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:00:22.000Z","msg":"狗鐵：唔好意思囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下午1時許，港島綫堅尼地城站與西營盤站之間，疑因有訊號故障，列車服務受阻。港鐵表示，港島綫列車預計需要額外行車時間，請為行程預留充裕時間。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵稱，港島綫列車服務調整如下：<br />\n<br />\n柴灣站和上環站之間，維持約五分鐘一班車；<br />\n上環和堅尼地城站之間，維持約二十分鐘一班車。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵正安排免費接駁巴士，行走堅尼地城至上環站，接載受影響乘客。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170804/57039900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170804%2F57039900&d=dqDVpvofywcWVKxrf4%2Bf2viMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=b781b05f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170804%2F57039900&h=e0849964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170804/57039900</a>"},{"pid":"89a60800902aecd9c442a632c194895ebcc1364d","tid":346612,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:00:39.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ab0f7c6ed0b02207f620ecb6dd4f519957e76a","tid":346612,"uid":82291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:00:52.000Z","msg":"係金鐘話等13分鐘先有車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db44a6b78c6b65ecfeaee1fa0062a625f1ec32cd","tid":346612,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:01:48.000Z","msg":"由於堅尼地城站和西營盤站之間有信號故障，港島綫列車駛經堅尼地城站和上環站路段時需要慢駛，港島綫來往堅尼地城站及柴灣站的行車時間預計需要額外10-15分鐘。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n港鐵免費接駁巴士將於稍後時間到達。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n現時港島綫月台上的乘客較多，候車時間亦會較長。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n請為行程預留充裕時間。"},{"pid":"59bdd6bfb22b8a31fd080decc26c928e2486c61f","tid":346612,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"送額外行車時間比你<br />\n比同一個價錢可以坐耐d<br />\n明益你"},{"pid":"6291f7367dcab0ed7674bf5cae2124ad9117b946","tid":346612,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:04:21.000Z","msg":"屌你老母前幾日好似荃灣綫連續故障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆街，我好日唔出九龍都奶左兩次野，兩日中哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ff73e686382d3fd1b331d2891a5e8f9091a585","tid":346612,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:07:13.000Z","msg":"仆街個廣播仲要把聲拆到仆街<br />\n唔撚上連登都唔知邊條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3e24899b2198bedb226d41677bc3b458e731f7","tid":346612,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:08:21.000Z","msg":"請保電車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60af0c89172377d01e1d251e2f833f97e9540f9","tid":346612,"uid":19552,"